        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>hair by form as material [300011821], hair (material) [300011814], hair and hair components as materials [300192982], keratinous material [300192973], animal material [300011793], biological material [300265629], materials by origin [300206573], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
